aften und Gesundheitsökonomie einen Überblick über Public Health relevante Inhalte ihrer Lehrgänge.  aThe third edition offers medical students and with students of public health, nursing, other health care professions, population scientists, and health economists an understandable introduction to the many aspects of public health. Along with basic terms and concepts, it imparts a basic understanding of the areas of prevention, health promotion, epidemiology, biostatistics, and the health care system.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Dez 2019) 4aBiostatistics. 4aBiostatistik. 4aEpidemiologie. 4aPrävention und Gesundheitsförderung. 4aPublic Health. 4aSozialmedizin. 4aepidemiology. 4aprevention and health promotion. 4apublic health. 4asocial medicine. 70(DE-601)10433181X0(DE-588)4047033-7aPräventivmedizin2gnd 70(DE-601)1045403110(DE-588)4139691-1aÖffentliches Gesundheitswesen2gnd 70(DE-601)1061566080(DE-588)4055860-5aSozialmedizin2gnd 7aMEDICAL / Public Health.2bisacsh1 aEgger, Matthias, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt.1 aRazum, Oliver, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt.1 aRieder, Anita, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2017z9783110548211oZDB-23-DPM0 cEPUBz97831104668810 cprintz978311046678240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110466867423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110466867.jpg  aEBA_CL_MDPM  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA14ALL  aPDA15STM  aPDA1ALL  aPDA3STM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DPMb2017